Zenit fans on the official site of the club declared the former captain of Team Russia as the best player of the past month.
In October, Arshavin took part in two matches in the group stage of the UEFA Champions League, three meets at the Russian championships and in a cup match.
He scored 2 assists.
Second place based on monthly results went to goalkeeper Yuri Lodygin, who became the best player of August and September.
The forward Khalk is in third place.
The Brazilian scored two goals and three assists.
Let us recall that Arshavin returned to "Zenit" this summer.
